OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHeavy rain sweeping
OL,6,Fsoutheastwards across Scotland and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland this morning,
OL,8,Freaching northern and western England
OL,9,Fand Wales this afternoon. Brighter,
OL,10,Fbut with patchy rain to the southeast.
OL,11,FTurning brighter, showery and colder
OL,12,Ffurther north. Windy, with gales in
OL,13,Fplaces.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FHeavy rain clearing southeast
OL,16,Facross England and Wales tonight.
OL,17,FOtherwise clear spells and showers,
OL,18,Fsome wintry. More persistent rain and
OL,19,Fsnow in the north, where patchy frost
OL,20,Fand ice. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
