OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cold and windy day with a
OL,6,Fmixture of sunshine and blustery
OL,7,Fshowers. Showers merging to give more
OL,8,Fpersistent rain and snow in places,
OL,9,Fthe snow most likely over hills.
